data.description: Beautifully Well Maintained Town-home On A Nice Tree Lined Street In Excellent Condition. Updated Kitchen With New Appliances . Separate  Breakfast Area That Can Also be used as a Mud Room . Large And Vast Living Room & Separate Dining room and Private Area With Fireplace . Exposed Brick And Hardwood Floors Through Out Home. 3 Large Bedrooms with 2 Being Masters. Large Bathroom with Jacuzzi tub and stand up shower. Ginormous Finished Basement that has the mechanical room with "like new" boiler and gas heater. New Washer & Dryer with 2 huge Rooms and large Bathroom & Own Separate Entrance. Shared Driveway W/ Private Garage. One block from public transportation and one block away from the Park. Walking distance to all.
